  "privacyPolicyTitle": "プライバシー Policy",
  "privacyLastUpdated": "Last updated: March 2025",
  "privacyIntro": "At {appName}, your プライバシー is paramount. This プライバシー Policy explains how we collect, use, store, and protect your personal and health-related data. By using our services, you agree to the practices described below.",
  "privacySectionDataCollection": "1. Data Collection",
  "privacyDataCollectionBody": "We collect the following categories of data: • Personal Information: N名前 メール address, 電話 number, 日付 of birth, and gender. • 健康 Data: Blood type, aアレルギー chronic conditions, m薬 vital signs, symptom logs, and トリアージ results. • 緊急 Contacts: Names, 電話 numbers, and relationships of your designated contacts. • Device Data: Device type, operating system, and app version for compatibility and sサポート • Usage Data: Feature interactions and anonymized analytics to improve our services. We only collect data that is necessary for providing our 健康 companion services. You have full control over what information you provide.",
  "privacySectionDataStorage": "2. Data Storage & Encryption",
  "privacyDataStorageBody": "Your data is stored using industry-leading security measures:\n\n• Encryption at Rest: All data stored in our databases is encrypted using AES-256 encryption.\n• Encryption in Transit: All data transmitted between your device and our servers uses TLS 1.3 encryption.\n• Health Passport: Your health passport data is encrypted with a unique key derived from your credentials.\n• QRコード Sharing: Shared health data via QR codes is encrypted and time-limited.\n• Infrastructure: Our servers are hosted in SOC 2 Type II certified data centers with 24/7 monitoring.\n\nWe do not store payment card information. All payment processing is handled by certified third-party providers.",
  "privacySectionGdpr": "3. GDPR Compliance",
  "privacyGdprBody": "{appName} is fully compliant with the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR): • Lawful Basis: We process your data based on your explicit consent and contractual necessity. • Data Minimization: We only collect and process data that is strictly necessary. • Purpose Limitation: Your data is used only for the purposes for which it was collected. • Right to Access: You can request a complete copy of your personal data at any t時間 • Right to Rectification: You can update or correct your data through the app s設定 • Right to Erasure: You can request complete deletion of your account and data. • Right to Portability: You can エクスポート your data in a machine-readable format. • Data Processing Agreements: すべて third-party processors have signed DPAs. • Cross-Border Transfers: Data is processed within the EU/EEA unless explicit consent is given otherwise.",
  "privacySectionYourRights": "4. Your Rights",
  "privacyRightsBody": "You have the following rights regarding your data: • Access: View すべて your personal and 健康 data within the app or request a data eエクスポート • Correction: 編集 your プロフィール information at any 時間 through 編集 Pプロフィール • Deletion: Request account deletion through 設定 > Data & プライバシー > 削除 Account. • Restriction: Limit how certain data is processed by adjusting your notification and sharing preferences. • Objection: Object to specific data processing activities by contacting our Data Protection Officer. • Withdrawal of Consent: You may withdraw consent at any 時間 without affecting the lawfulness of prior processing. To exercise any of these rights, contact us at privacy@vitalseker.com or through the in-app サポート feature.",
  "privacySectionContactUs": "5. 連絡 Us",
  "privacyContactBody": "If you have any questions or concerns 概要 this プライバシー Policy or our data practices, please contact us: • Eメール privacy@vitalseker.com • Sサポート support@vitalseker.com • Data Protection Officer: dpo@vitalseker.com • Address: {producer}, Data Protection Office We aim to respond to すべて privacy-related inquiries within 30 days.",
